{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play Word Chain Solo or with a Friend!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Connect words that match the illustrations shown on the panels to create a word chain! Since there might be multiple words to describe each illustration, unexpected connections could emerge...?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not only can you play word chain by yourself, but you can also enjoy a versus mode with two players! Try to read your opponent's mind as you flip through the panels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Flip through as many panels as you can within the time limit and aim for a top ranking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385250/extras/ContentExample000.png?t=1736416628\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Meet &quot;Laby&quot; - Your Word Chain Buddy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your word chain companion is Laby, a squishy yellow robot who came from somewhere unknown. Laby is very knowledgeable and will teach you all sorts of words!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385250/extras/\u30b3\u30df\u30e5\u30cb\u30c6\u30a3\u30a2\u30a4\u30b3\u30f3.png?t=1736416628\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Discover Lots of New Words Through Word Chain</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the &quot;Picture Dictionary,&quot; you can review all the illustrations and words you've uncovered from previous panels! The more words you collect, the easier it will become to make word chain connections.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3385250/extras/ContentExample002.png?t=1736416628\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Friend Features (Coming Soon)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A friend feature is planned for a future update. Compet